    "Martin Viessmann is president of Viessmann Group, a German manufacturer of heating, refrigeration and climate-control equipment.",
    "He is the grandson of founder Johann Viessmann. The private company has 12,000 employees and 23 production divisions in 12 countries.",
    "Martin envisions a world where CO2 emissions are reduced by 80% and the consumption of fossil energy by two-thirds.",
    "In 2012, the company received the Energy Globe Award for Sustainability in the \"Air\" category. In 2013 Martin was named Greentech Manager of the Year.",
    "In 2017, at age 28, son Maximilian was named co-CEO of the company."
  ],
